 <div class="features">
 <div class="wrapper">
 <h1 id="features" class="anchor"></h1>
 <h1> cute, intuitive &amp; easy-to-use ui </h1> 
 <h2> With no useless buttons or features, Unlazify aims to make you as productive as possible. </h2> 
 <div class="row-fluid">
 
 <!--###   Feature 7 ###-->
 <div class="span4 featu">
 <div class="icon"> <img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft1 sprite feature7" alt=""><img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft2 sprite feature7-hover" alt="" style="opacity: 0;"> </div>
 <h1> Repeating tasks</h1>
 <p> Repetition is the key to success in any activity. Easily set your recurring tasks and Unlazify will automatically create them for you on the selected days. </p>
 </div>
 
 <!--###   Feature 1 ###-->
 <div class="span4 featu">
 <div class="icon"> <img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft1 sprite feature1-sprite" alt=""><img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft2 sprite feature1-hover-sprite" alt=""> </div>
 <h1> Subtasks</h1>
 <p> Some tasks may be abstract or not specific, e.g. projects. Splitting such tasks into specific subtasks is a great way how not to get stuck. </p>
 </div>
 
  <!--###   Feature 2 ###-->
 <div class="span4 featu">
 <div class="icon"> <img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft1 sprite feature2-sprite" alt=""><img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft2 sprite feature2-hover-sprite" alt=""> </div>
 <h1> Progress bar</h1>
 <p> As you add or complete tasks, the progress bar beneath your to-do list dynamically updates and changes its color based on the progress. </p>
 </div>
 
 </div>
 
 <div class="row-fluid">
 
   <!--###   Feature 3 ###-->
 <div class="span4 featu">
 <div class="icon"> <img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft1 sprite feature3-sprite" alt=""><img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft2 sprite feature3-hover-sprite" alt="" style="opacity: 0;"> </div>
 <h1> Printing tasks</h1>
 <p> Do you prefer paper? Or like ticking by pen? Printing tasks is so easy with Unlazify. </p>
 </div>
 
  <!--###   Feature 4 ###-->
 <div class="span4 featu">
 <div class="icon"> <img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft1 sprite feature4-sprite" alt=""><img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft2 sprite feature4-hover-sprite" alt=""> </div>
 <h1> Talking characters</h1>
 <p> Unlazify introduces a unique feature - talking characters. The idea is to invoke emotions by encouraging or discouraging, which will keep you motivated! If you find your Blop annoying, you can disable it in the settings. </p>
 </div>
 
  <!--###   Feature 5 ###-->
 <div class="span4 featu">
 <div class="icon"> <img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft1 sprite feature5-sprite" alt=""><img src="./Unlazify - Personal to-do list and task manager_files/blank.png" class="ft2 sprite feature5-hover-sprite" alt=""> </div>
 <h1> Mobile apps (coming soon)</h1>
 <p> Sync all to-do lists and tasks between your PC and mobile devices with one simple click. Mobile apps will be released for iOS and Android platforms. </p>
 </div>
 
  <!--###   Feature 6 ###-->
