	 <div class="span4 featu">
	 <div class="icon"> <img src="/images/blank.png" class="ft1 sprite feature6-sprite" alt="" /><img src="/images/blank.png" class="ft2 sprite feature6-hover-sprite" alt=""/> </div>
	 <h1> Customization (coming soon)</h1>
	 <p> Adapt Unlazify to your preferences. You can change background and color scheme. </p>
